OL,3,CCalls to revisit assisted dying debate
OL,4,Cin Guernsey
OL,6,FA Guernsey woman is calling for the
OL,7,Fisland to revisit the topic of
OL,8,Flegalising assisted dying following
OL,9,Frecent legislation across the British
OL,10,FIsles
OL,12,FJulie's husband - Guy - was terminally
OL,13,Fill and chose to end his life legally
OL,14,Fin Spain two years ago.
OL,16,FShe now wants politicians to debate
OL,17,Fthe topic again - after a previous
OL,18,Fproposition failed six years ago.
