OL,3,CCalls to revisit assisted dying debate
OL,4,Cin Guernsey
OL,6,FJulie explains: "It should be debated
OL,7,Fagain here in Guernsey, and it would
OL,8,Fmake my day if it did go through."
OL,10,FIt comes as UK MPs voted in favour of
OL,11,Fa bill that would legalise assisted
OL,12,Fdying for people who are terminally
OL,13,Fill in England and Wales on Friday 29
OL,14,FNovember.
OL,16,FThey follow Jersey who voted to allow
OL,17,Fpeople who have a terminal illness to
OL,18,Fend their lives with the help of
OL,19,Fmedical professionals on Wednesday 22
OL,20,FMay.
