OL,3,CCalls to revisit assisted dying debate
OL,4,Cin Guernsey
OL,6,FIn 2018, States of Guernsey members
OL,7,Frejected Deputy Gavin St Pier's
OL,8,Fproposition - then Chief Minister - to
OL,9,Flegalise assisted dying.
OL,11,FIt would have made Guernsey the first
OL,12,Fplace in the British Isles to do so.
OL,14,FAnd now, Deputy St Pier has voiced his
OL,15,Finterest in requesting a new requete
OL,16,Fin 2025.
OL,18,FJulie says that Guy had an asbestos-
OL,19,Frelated cancer when he decided to seek
OL,20,Fto end his life legally.
