OL,3,CCalls to revisit assisted dying debate
OL,4,Cin Guernsey
OL,6,FShe explains: "There wasn't anything
OL,7,Fthat they could do operation-wise
OL,8,F(...) he was literally given three
OL,9,Fmonths to live.
OL,11,F"He said 'Come sit with me a minute.
OL,12,FI'm going to ask you two things. One
OL,13,Fis, please don't talk me out of it
OL,14,Fthis time, and the second one is be
OL,15,Fstrong.'
OL,17,F"And I was the strongest person on
OL,18,FEarth.
OL,20,F"This is all about choice - his
OL,21,Fchoice. To him, it was everything."
