OL,3,CCalls to revisit assisted dying debate
OL,4,Cin Guernsey
OL,6,FDeputy Gavin St Pier has made no
OL,7,Fsecret of the fact that he intends to
OL,8,Fbring back debate on assisted dying.
OL,10,FIt's expected that this will come
OL,11,Fearly next year via a requete.
OL,13,FIt would mean that a decision will be
OL,14,Fmade on this issue before the end of
OL,15,Fthis political term, just months
OL,16,Fbefore a new group of deputies take
OL,17,Foffice.
