OL,3,CCalls to revisit assisted dying debate
OL,4,Cin Guernsey
OL,6,FAfter 2018's defeat, Guernsey was
OL,7,Falways going to end up following other
OL,8,Fjurisdictions. The UK and Jersey have
OL,9,Fmade their stance clear, as has the
OL,10,FIsle of Man.
OL,12,FThe jurisdictions we are always
OL,13,Fcompared to have moved on.
OL,15,FDespite well-worn arguments about
OL,16,Fsafeguards and the size of our
OL,17,Fjurisdiction being aired, it would be
OL,18,Fincredibly strange for Guernsey to not
OL,19,Ffollow suit.
